headline: Is Vision Capital Fund’s Investment Thesis for The Trade Desk (TTD) Aligned with The CEO’s Strategy?
summary: Vision Capital Fund, an investment management company, released its third-quarter 2025 investor letter. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here. The fund returned +15.6% net, YTD, compared to +14.8% for the S&P 500 for the same period. Since its inception on October 1, 2024, the fund has returned a cumulative of +27.8% net, […]
